=== 法國青年國家隊 ===
2015年6月17日，斯帕拉尼亞成為法國 U20的隊長，並在{{link-en|2015年土伦杯国际足球邀请赛|2015 Toulon Tournament}}決賽對陣摩洛哥 U20時，接應{{link-en|羅曼·夏拜恩|Romain Habran}}的角球射進反超前的1球，帶領球隊以3比1贏下比賽，奪得自2008年後首個[[土伦杯国际足球邀请赛|土伦杯国际足球邀请赛]]冠軍<ref name="frenchfootballweekly">{{cite news|last= Smith|first= Jeremy (8 June 2015)|url= http://frenchfootballweekly.com/2015/06/08/france-weather-moroccan-storm-to-lift-the-toulon-trophy/|title= France Weather Moroccan Storm to Lift the Toulon trophy|website= French Football Weekly|accessdate= 2015-11-14|language= en|archive-date= 2016-03-05|archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20160305024615/http://frenchfootballweekly.com/2015/06/08/france-weather-moroccan-storm-to-lift-the-toulon-trophy/|dead-url= no}}</ref><ref name="outsideoftheboot">{{cite news|last= Bekker|first= Liam|date= 2015-12-22|url= http://outsideoftheboot.com/2015/12/22/scout-report-stephane-sparagna-marseille/|title= Scout Report: Stephane Sparagna: Marseille's combative young centre-back|website= Outside of the Boot|accessdate= 2015-12-22|language= en|archive-date= 2015-12-22|archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20151222235300/http://outsideoftheboot.com/2015/12/22/scout-report-stephane-sparagna-marseille/|dead-url= no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.rsssf.com/tablest/toulon.html|title=Tournoi Espoirs de Toulon|website=Rec Sport Soccer Statistics Foundation|accessdate=2016-08-18|language=en|archive-date=2018-10-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181002155844/http://rsssf.com/tablest/toulon.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。除了決賽攻入1球外，他亦揭幕戰對陣美國 U20時，亦射進一記自由球<ref name="USSoccer">{{cite news|last=|first=|title=U-23 MNT Falls to Host France in Toulon Tournament Opener|url=http://www.ussoccer.com/stories/2015/05/27/16/43/150527-u23mnt-loses-to-france-at-toulon|website=US Soccer|date=2015-05-27|accessdate=2015-11-27|language=en|archive-date=2015-11-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151108025151/http://www.ussoccer.com/stories/2015/05/27/16/43/150527-u23mnt-loses-to-france-at-toulon|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

在U20取得成功後，斯帕拉尼亞獲法國 U21徵召，並於2015年11月15日對陣[[馬其頓21歲以下國家足球隊|馬其頓 U21]]時首次為法國 U21上陣，但他在比賽中兩黃一紅被逐離場，最終球隊以2比2戰和對手<ref name="Macedonian Football">{{cite news|last= Zlateski|first= Alexander|date= 2015-11-23|url= http://www.macedonianfootball.com/index.php?option=com_content&view=article&id=7897:france-u21-fights-back-to-draw-macedonia&catid=13:international&Itemid=64|title= French rally holds Macedonia U21 to a draw|website= Macedonian Football|accessdate= 2015-11-23|language= en|archive-date= 2015-11-17|archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20151117122732/http://www.macedonianfootball.com/index.php?option=com_content&view=article&id=7897:france-u21-fights-back-to-draw-macedonia&catid=13:international&Itemid=64|dead-url= no}}</ref>。

